    "description": "Don Bosco Tech Consulting Pvt Ltd, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Subject Matter Expert for our Thane operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Don Bosco Tech Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nDon Bosco Tech Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in IB Curriculum\n• Proficiency in Special Education\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Thane, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Don Bosco Tech Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
